    "name": "Goldilock One: The Mists of Jakaíra Demo",
    "steam_appid": 3202170,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202170/extras/f2712ebb76f795bf077e1623585a8874.poster.avif?t=1764760273\" width=620 height=178 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202170/extras/f2712ebb76f795bf077e1623585a8874.webm?t=1764760273\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202170/extras/f2712ebb76f795bf077e1623585a8874.mp4?t=1764760273\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关于试玩版</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >试玩版从特农德村开始，你需要完成任务来解锁武器，这将使你能够探索村庄大门外的危险并猎杀生物。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >之后，找到进入贾卡伊拉祭坛的路，进入其秘密地牢，那里充满了具有挑战性的生物，最后是一场与感染的巨人墨克斯佩尔的boss战，这是一项被困在地牢深处的活体实验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202170/extras/6dfa6693865a343172f699a7a479a55f.avif?t=1764760273\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202170/extras_big/6dfa6693865a343172f699a7a479a55f.avif?t=1764760273 width=800 height=266 /></span><strong>Goldilock One: 贾凯拉的迷雾</strong> 是一款动作角色扮演游戏，将玩家带到一个遥远星球最黑暗、最寒冷的监狱。 在这个敌对且无情的环境中生存于大规模战斗中，结成联盟，寻找你被流放的答案。  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >探索并面对奈贝加德的危险</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在一个寒冷的星球的外部不适宜生存的监狱中，那些最恶劣的罪犯被送到这里，记忆被抹去。 冒险前行，沉浸于一个充满困境和选择的密集剧情中，揭示一个你之前未知的现实的不同面貌，同时尝试理解你被流放的原因。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202170/extras/6a94dc0269acb833740f86608aba1e2f.poster.avif?t=1764760273\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202170/extras/6a94dc0269acb833740f86608aba1e2f.webm?t=1764760273\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202170/extras/6a94dc0269acb833740f86608aba1e2f.mp4?t=1764760273\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >掌握战斗技巧</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战斗需要策略和技能，<strong>Goldilock One</strong> 提供了独特的混合体验，结合了对抗多个敌人的砍杀战斗和更节奏缓慢的时刻，面对挑战性敌人时需要更多的自我保护。  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202170/extras/b36785b20b1e485c5aa4f275cb5787b5.poster.avif?t=1764760273\" width=600 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202170/extras/b36785b20b1e485c5aa4f275cb5787b5.webm?t=1764760273\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202170/extras/b36785b20b1e485c5aa4f275cb5787b5.mp4?t=1764760273\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >建立联盟</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与各种NPC发展关系；根据你的决定，有些NPC可能会成为你的冒险伙伴。 实时切换他们之间的控制，访问独特的挑战和以前无法进入的区域。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202170/extras/fbf274570d6c1c7783942cee0a7757d1.avif?t=1764760273\" width=600 height=268 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >生存</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收集和掠夺资源，用于与NPC一起制作的合成配方。如果管理得当，这些成果将为你的旅程带来诸多优势，包括药水、食物，甚至装备。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202170/extras/e7d408fc33783d8a709739c52741f24c.poster.avif?t=1764760273\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202170/extras/e7d408fc33783d8a709739c52741f24c.webm?t=1764760273\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202170/extras/e7d408fc33783d8a709739c52741f24c.mp4?t=1764760273\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >强化你的装备</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用恩斯基塔水晶为你的装备注入特殊属性。将其镶嵌到可用的插槽中，你将看到效果，不仅体现在装备的属性上（伤害类型、防御等），还体现在攻击时的视觉效果上。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202170/extras/c4333f3a5d0b09e9da14262db9e74dd2.poster.avif?t=1764760273\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202170/extras/c4333f3a5d0b09e9da14262db9e74dd2.webm?t=1764760273\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202170/extras/c4333f3a5d0b09e9da14262db9e74dd2.mp4?t=1764760273\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >面对独特的敌人</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >挑战从新星球的本土生物到基因改造生物，甚至是未来机器的各种生物。 遇见受不同文化和巴西民俗启发的神话元素创造物。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >单人挑战或合作游戏</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >独自接受这个挑战，或通过邀请朋友一起玩本地或在线分屏多人游戏（通过 Remote Play Together）来享受团队时刻。  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202170/extras/d40432c578ed30ad6added4f2b44509d.poster.avif?t=1764760273\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202170/extras/d40432c578ed30ad6added4f2b44509d.webm?t=1764760273\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3202170/extras/d40432c578ed30ad6added4f2b44509d.mp4?t=1764760273\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>开放世界与探索：</strong> 奈贝加德是一个广阔的领域，充满了危险和神秘。 探索多样化的环境，发现秘密，并与NPC建立联盟，以提高你的生存机会。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>团队系统与合作：</strong> 控制你团队中的不同成员，每个成员都有独特的能力，可以组合起来克服挑战和解决复杂的谜题。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>独特的图形与设计：</strong> 一种将现实元素与卡通渲染艺术风格相结合的视觉风格，唤起了图画小说和漫画的美学。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>动态叙事与困境系统：</strong> 你的决策塑造了你周围的世界。 游戏的困境系统提供多种完成任务和解决谜题的方法，结果深刻影响故事的发展。</p>",
